data_findings.finding: Key feature engineering: Title extraction from Name (Mr, Mrs, Miss, Master, etc.), FamilySize = SibSp + Parch + 1, IsAlone = FamilySize == 1, Age binning, Fare binning. Best submission score ~0.78 using hard voting ensemble of tuned classifiers.
